727376f-a.title: Queens: Merrick Boulevard - Liberty Avenue
727376f-a.text:
Merri:k Boulevard, east side, between Liberty and 104th Avenues,
showing two combined frame dwellings with entrances at both ends.
Note the barn to the left of the house.
P. L. Sperr  March 30, 1932
NO REPRODUCTIOIS
